\c 17
\s UMika lendlu yakhe yezithombe
\p
\v 1 Kwakukhona-ke umuntu wentabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + 17.8. Josh. 24.33.\x*, obizo lakhe lalinguMika\x + 17.4. 1 Kho. 22. 8.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesithi kunina: Izinhlamvu zesiliva eziyinkulungwane lekhulu ezathathwa kuwe, owaqalekisa ngazo, njalo wakhuluma endlebeni zami, khangela, leyomali ikimi, mina ngayithatha. Unina wasesithi: Kawubusiswe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ndodana yami\x + 1 Sam. 15.13.\x*.
\v 3 Wathi esezibuyisele kunina izinhlamvu eziyinkulungwane lekhulu zesiliva, unina wathi: Ngasengisehlukanisile lokusehlukanisela iN\nd kosi\nd* isiliva sami sivela esandleni sami sibe ngesendodana yami, ukuze ngenze isithombe esibaziweyo\x + Eks. 20.4.\x* lesithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + Levi 19.4.\x*. Khathesi-ke ngizasibuyisela kuwe.
\v 4 Kodwa wayibuyisela imali kunina. Unina wasethatha izinhlamvu zesiliva ezingamakhulu amabili, wazinika umkhandi\x + Isa. 40.19. 46.6.\x*, owenza ngazo isithombe esibaziweyo\x + Eks. 20.4.\x* lesithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + Levi 19.4.\x*; zasezisiba sendlini kaMika\x + 17.4. 1 Kho. 22.8.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo lowomuntu uMika wayelendlu yabonkulunkulu, wenza \w i-efodi\w**\x + 8.27. 18.14,17.\x* lamatherafi\x + Gen. 31.19.\x*, wehlukanisa omunye wamadodana akhe, ukuze abe ngumpristi wakhe.
\v 6 Ngalezonsuku kwakungelankosi koIsrayeli\x + 18.1. 19.1. 21.25.\x*; wonke umuntu wayesenza okwakulungile emehlweni akhe\x + 21.25. Dute. 12.8.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Njalo kwakukhona ijaha leBhethelehema-Juda\x + 12.8,10. 19.1. Gen. 35.19, Josh. 19.15.\x*, elosendo lukaJuda, elalingumLevi, njalo lahlala njengowezizwe khona.
\v 8 Lowomuntu wasesuka emzini, eBhethelehema-Juda, ukuyahlala njengowezizwe lapho ayengathola khona \add indawo\add*. Wafika entabeni yakoEfrayimi, endlini kaMika\x + 17.8. Josh. 24.33.\x*, ehamba ngendlela yakhe.
\v 9 UMika wasesithi kuye: Uvela ngaphi? Wasesithi kuye: NgingumLevi weBhethelehema-Juda, ngiya ukuyahlala njengowezizwe lapho engingathola khona \add indawo\add*.
\v 10 UMika wasesithi kuye: Hlala lami, ube kimi\x + 18.19.\x* ngubaba lompristi\x + 18.19. Gen. 45.8. 2 Kho. 5.13.\x*, mina ngizakunika izinhlamvu zesiliva ezilitshumi ngomnyaka\x + 11.40.\x*, lezigqoko zokugqoka, lokudla kwakho. UmLevi wasengena.
\v 11 UmLevi wavuma ukuhlala lalowomuntu; njalo ijaha laba kuye njengomunye wamadodana akhe\x + Eks. 2.21.\x*.
\v 12 UMika wamehlukanisa umLevi\x + 17.5.\x*, ijaha laselisiba ngumpristi wakhe\x + 18.30.\x*, laba sendlini kaMika.
\v 13 UMika wasesithi: Khathesi ngiyazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izangenzela okuhle, ngoba ngilomLevi ongumpristi.